name: AskTheIntern
tag_list: internship, resume, cover-letter, advice, wall-street, consulting, finance, marketing, public-relations, communications, engineering
overview:
AskTheIntern.com helps undergraduate college students find internships, rate internships and learn more about the internship process.

By providing students with comprehensive internship ratings submitted by their peers, the internship search process is simplified. Students find the answers to the questions that they would never be able to ask during the interview process such as; How much will I be paid? How many hours will I work? Will I be completing meaningful work? What percentage of interns get hired Full-Time?

AskTheIntern.com is student’s #1 internship community.
